<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>We heard you forgot your password</h1>
    
    <p>Dear, <%= @user.username %></p>
    
    <p>We got a request to reset your password. To do that now, <%= link_to 'click here', edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>.</p>
    
    <p>Have a great day,<br>Streeetball</p>
    
    <p><small>If you did not request your password to be reset, just ignore this email and your password will stay the same.</small></p>
  </body>
</html>